high_descs: Go forward, then turn right, then turn left, then turn right again to approach the table.
Pick up the nearest tomato on the table.
Go to the sink to your right.
Wash the tomato in the sink.
Turn around and go to the table behind you.
Put the tomato on the table behind the bread and in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the large wooden table
Pick up the tomato behind the nearest salt shaker from the table
Turn right and walk up to the kitchen sink
Wash the tomato in the sink under water then remove it
Turn around and walk back to face the large wooden table
Put the tomato on the table just in front of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the washed tomato on the table

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the table
Grab the tomato on the table,
Turn right, walk to the sink
Put the tomato in the sink, turn on the faucet, wash the tomato, turn off the faucet, take the tomato out
Turn around, walk to the table
Put the tomato on the table
anns.task_desc: wash the tomato from the table, put it back on the table

high_descs: Turn around and go across to the brown table.
Pick up the tomato from the right side of the table.
Carry the tomato and turn right to go to the sink.
Place the tomato in the sink and turn on the water. Turn the water off and pick up the tomato.
Carry the tomato and turn around. Go back to the brown table on the right.
Place the tomato on the table, behind the loaf of bread on the left side.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a tomato and place it on the table.
